            "UserStoryLink": "\"Error handling for Data File filename changes\", https://extron.atlassian.net/browse/TOOL-4287 ",
            "UserStory": "TOOL-4287: As a Control System Programmer or AV Technician, I want to be notified when CSDU can’t access project resources (or can’t find them), So that I won’t have to force close the app and re-select my project.  ",
            "TaskLink": "\"Task Issue: TOOL-4318\", https://extron.atlassian.net/browse/TOOL-4318 ",
            "TestCaseLink": "\"Test Case: TOOL-T4655\", https://extron.atlassian.net/projects/TOOL?selectedItem=com.atlassian.plugins.atlassian-connect-plugin:com.kanoah.test-manager__main-project-page#!/testCase/TOOL-T4655 ",
            "ProjectFile": "DeployProject\\systeminfo.json"
